                                    </p>
                                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mt-2 text-xs">
                                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-2 rounded">Single-mode: 9μm core, laser, long distance</div>
                                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-2 rounded">Multi-mode: 50/62.5μm, LED, short distance</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2">
